snippet.textDisplay: All you people saying that they threatened him have no idea what they were actually saying! The ONLY thing they were saying is that IF he talks about the candy he should mention that it was free. NOT that he HAS to mention the candy AT ALL! He could have received the gift and worn the shoes and ate the candy and never said anything about it.  It's the same thing as when any YouTuber makes content about a product that they were payed for.  It's called transparency and it is a good thing!
